com.fxgraph.edges

Class MessageEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fxgraph.edges.AbstractEdge
      • com.fxgraph.edges.MessageEdge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEdge, IGraphNode, SequenceDiagram.IMessageEdge

    public class MessageEdge
extends AbstractEdge
implements SequenceDiagram.IMessageEdge
    A fully defined AbstractEdge implementation specialized for representing sequence diagram messages.

    A message edge has a name and a y offset, and is always represented as a directed horizontal line between actor life-lines.
    Author:
    sirolf2009, ogallagher (javadoc)
    See Also:
    SequenceDiagram, SequenceDiagram.IMessageEdge
